==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-iːtəs|-iːtəs]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun|es}}

#{{cattag|US|biology}} An unborn or unhatched vertibrate that is showing signs of the mature animal; an unborn baby after the 7th week of gestation.

